---
// DALILI · Notre histoire — the founders' manifesto

const founders = [
  {
    name: 'Aymane Amri',
    role: 'Full-Stack · IA · Communication',
    bio: "La machine qui code de l'aube à la nuit. Quand Aymane prend un sujet, il l'amène jusqu'au bout — IA, infrastructure, com'.",
    hue: 220,
    initials: 'AA',
  },
  {
    name: 'Mouad Mousmih',
    role: 'Full-Stack · DevOps · Expert IA',
    bio: "Le cerveau architectural. Mouad pense système, performance, fiabilité. C'est lui qui s'assure que tout tient quand ça scale.",
    hue: 280,
    initials: 'MM',
  },
  {
    name: 'Mouhcine Mellouk',
    role: 'Marketing · UX/UI · SEO · DA',
    bio: "Le front. La voix. L'œil. C'est Mouhcine qui décide comment DALILI parle au monde et à quoi ça ressemble.",
    hue: 30,
    initials: 'MM',
  },
];
---

<section class="dl-story" id="story">
  <!-- Atmospheric backdrop -->
  <div class="dl-story-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="dl-story-head">
      <div class="dl-eyebrow reveal">Notre histoire</div>
      <h2 class="dl-story-title reveal reveal-delay-1">
        On a vécu l'expatriation.<br/>
        <em>On en a fait une mission.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Editorial manifesto -->
    <div class="dl-story-manifesto">
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        On sait ce que ça coûte de débarquer seul·e dans un pays où personne ne t'attend.
        Les démarches qui paraissent simples mais qui te font perdre tes mois. Les soirées où tu cherches
        juste quelqu'un à qui parler dans ta langue. Cette sensation de devoir tout réinventer, tout seul.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <strong>DALILI, c'est l'app qu'on aurait voulu avoir.</strong>
        Un guide pour les démarches. Un toit chez quelqu'un qui te ressemble.
        Une communauté qui t'attend avant même que tu n'arrives.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The team -->
    <div class="dl-story-team-header reveal">
      <div class="dl-eyebrow">L'équipe</div>
      <h3 class="dl-h3">Trois esprits, une mission.</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="dl-story-team">
      {founders.map((f, i) => (
        <article class={`dl-founder reveal reveal-delay-${i + 1}`} style={`--hue: ${f.hue}`}>
          <div class="dl-founder-avatar">
            <div class="dl-founder-avatar-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <span>{f.initials}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="dl-founder-content">
            <h4 class="dl-founder-name">{f.name}</h4>
            <div class="dl-founder-role">{f.role}</div>
            <p class="dl-founder-bio">{f.bio}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="dl-founder-corner" aria-hidden="true">0{i + 1}</div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Brothers manifesto -->
    <blockquote class="dl-story-quote reveal">
      <span class="dl-quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
      <p>
        On est des <em>frères</em> avant tout, et on le restera toujours.<br/>
        Le projet ne passera jamais au-dessus de ça.
      </p>
      <footer>— Le manifeste DALILI</footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dl-story {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(100px, 14vw, 200px) 0;
    background: var(--dl-cream);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .dl-story-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(700px 480px at 10% 20%, rgba(1, 77, 248, 0.06), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(600px 400px at 90% 80%, rgba(122, 92, 245, 0.05), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Head */
  .dl-story-head {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .dl-story-head .dl-eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--dl-blue);
  }
  .dl-story-title {
    font-family: var(--dl-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 78px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--dl-ink);
  }
  .dl-story-title em {
    font-family: var(--dl-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dl-blue);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* Manifesto */
  .dl-story-manifesto {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 0 120px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .dl-story-manifesto p {
    font-family: var(--dl-body);
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.4vw, 21px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--dl-ink-2);
  }
  .dl-story-manifesto p strong {
    color: var(--dl-ink);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Team header */
  .dl-story-team-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .dl-story-team-header .dl-eyebrow { color: var(--dl-ink-3); }

  /* Team grid */
  .dl-story-team {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .dl-founder {
    position: relative;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(1,77,248,0.10), 0 8px 32px -10px rgba(1,77,248,0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-out), box-shadow 0.4s var(--ease-out);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .dl-founder:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(1,77,248,0.25), 0 24px 60px -16px rgba(1,77,248,0.22);
  }
  .dl-founder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%; right: -30%;
    width: 240px; height: 240px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, hsla(var(--hue), 75%, 60%, 0.15), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: transform 0.6s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .dl-founder:hover::before { transform: scale(1.4) translate(-20px, 20px); }

  /* Founder avatar */
  .dl-founder-avatar {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--dl-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(var(--hue), 75%, 62%), hsl(calc(var(--hue) + 40), 70%, 42%));
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px -10px hsla(var(--hue), 75%, 50%, 0.5);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .dl-founder-avatar-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 25%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), transparent 55%);
  }
  .dl-founder-avatar span { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* Founder content */
  .dl-founder-name {
    font-family: var(--dl-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: var(--dl-ink);
  }
  .dl-founder-role {
    font-family: var(--dl-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: hsl(var(--hue), 65%, 45%);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .dl-founder-bio {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--dl-ink-2);
  }
  .dl-founder-corner {
    position: absolute;
    top: 22px; right: 24px;
    font-family: var(--dl-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--dl-ink-4);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Quote */
  .dl-story-quote {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .dl-quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: var(--dl-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 120px;
    color: var(--dl-blue);
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.2;
  }
  .dl-story-quote p {
    font-family: var(--dl-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--dl-ink);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .dl-story-quote em {
    color: var(--dl-blue);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .dl-story-quote footer {
    font-family: var(--dl-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dl-ink-3);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .dl-story-team {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .dl-story-manifesto { margin-bottom: 80px; }
    .dl-story-team { margin-bottom: 80px; }
  }
</style>
